{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#6997: onServerPrefetch produces an invalid warning on ssr",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:25:29.905210+00:00",
  "text": "onServerPrefetch produces an invalid warning on ssr\n\n### Vue version\r\n\r\n3\r\n\r\n### Link to minimal reproduction\r\n\r\nhttps://sfc.vuejs.org/#__SSR__\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1.  In `Setup()`,  define `const data = ref(false)`;\r\n2.  In the `onServerPrefetch`  life Lifecycle, set the `data.value = true`;\r\n3. Get the `data` in the template is false;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\n\r\n`data.value` is `true`\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\n\r\n`data.value` is `false`\r\n\r\n### System Info\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Any additional comments?\r\nhttps://vuejs.org/api/composition-api-lifecycle.html#onserverprefetch\r\n_No response_",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    ":lady_beetle:  bug",
    "scope: ssr"
  ],
